rComments: Easy A! The class could be a lot more fun if whites/Asians/Hispanics etc were in it. Easy assignments. Have to read two easy books, but we go over them in class. Got to connect with other people too. Cool class.

I love this class! It's soooo easy! We only meet once a week, and we only have to dress up like 3-5 times during the semester. You'll get to connect with other students (mostly black), but people from other races actually make the class a lot more interesting! It's an easy A, and offers over 150 extra credit points! (you can't beat that). Take it!

WORST CLASS EVER. PROFESSOR IS UNORGANIZED. ASSIGNMENTS ARE MEANINGLESS TO THE CLASS. UNFAIR GRADER. BORING. MAKES STUDENTS DRESS UP FOR CLASS ON RANDOM DAYS. QUIZZES AND TESTS BASED OFF CONTEMPORARY AFRICAN AMERICAN MOVIES. I DO NOT RECOMMEND.
